reet, Kirikiri Industrial Layout, Apapa, Lagos and put up a notice for staff and… December 14, 2019 In "News" The Sun Publishing Limited has prayed the Abuja division of the Court of Appeal to restrain the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission, EFCC, or its agents from sealing off its premises pending the hearing and determination of its appeal before the court. June 13, 2017 In "News" The management of the Sun Publishing Limited and the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission have disagreed on the visit of the anti-crime agency to the company’s head office in Lagos on Monday. June 12, 2017 In "News"